OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FSir Sadiq Khan has announced a #7
OL,8,Fmillion campaign to showcase London to
OL,9,Fthe world and tackle online
OL,10,F"disinformation" that he says is
OL,11,Fharming the capital's reputation.
OL,13,FThe Mayor of London said the city had
OL,14,Fbeen subjected to a "relentless and
OL,15,Funprecedented attack of lies and
OL,16,Fhatred" on social media, describing
OL,17,Fonline disinformation as a "global
OL,18,Fscourge".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@PO]vD@UOUxD@GO]yD@\OUzD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
