OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781536274
OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FThe campaign, to be delivered by
OL,8,FLondon & Partners, will launch in
OL,9,FSeptember and target audiences across
OL,10,FEurope, the United States and Asia.
OL,12,FIt aims to promote the capital by
OL,13,Fcelebrating London's "rich heritage,
OL,14,Fworld-class experiences, culture,
OL,15,Fcreativity and role as a centre for
OL,16,Finnovation and trade".
OL,26,@uD@VOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
