OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781536274
OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FA report published by the Greater
OL,8,FLondon Authority (GLA) earlier this
OL,9,Fyear found a nearly 200% increase over
OL,10,Fthe past two years in social media
OL,11,Fposts portraying London as dangerous
OL,12,For in decline.
OL,14,FSir Sadiq said: "We are facing a
OL,15,Frelentless and unprecedented attack of
OL,16,Flies and hatred from those wanting to
OL,17,Fdamage our capital's standing and our
OL,18,Fhugely important tourism industry.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781536274
OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,F"Disinformation about London has
OL,8,Fbecome a truly global scourge. It's a
OL,9,Fmoney-making industry pushing lies
OL,10,Fabout our capital and preying on
OL,11,Fpeople's fears around the world, so we
OL,12,Fmust fight back on a global scale.
OL,14,F"That's why we're creating this major
OL,15,Fnew campaign to challenge these false
OL,16,Fnarratives and demonstrate once again
OL,17,Fwhy there's no better place in the
OL,18,Fworld than London."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
