PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781536274
OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FA new GLA report found that social
OL,8,Fmedia users in Asia are being targeted
OL,9,Fby "disinformation" about London.
OL,11,FIt found that in some months, more
OL,12,Fthan 15,000 posts have been posted on
OL,13,FX in Japanese with claims that the
OL,14,Fcapital is lawless and under the
OL,15,Finfluence of Islamic governance.
OL,17,FThe report said that one account used
OL,18,FAI imagery to falsely claim that
OL,19,Fmillions of people attended Unite The
OL,20,FKingdom rally organised by activist
OL,21,FTommy Robinson.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
