OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump has
OL,8,Fpreviously accused Sir Sadiq of doing
OL,9,Fa "terrible job", adding that "crime
OL,10,Fin London is through the roof", in
OL,11,Ftheir long-running war of words.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police said in
OL,14,FJanuary that the homicide rate in
OL,15,FLondon dropped to its lowest in 11
OL,16,Fyears in 2025.
OL,26,@qD@COUqD@PO]qD@_OUrD@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
