CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781536274
OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FBut the force has some of the highest
OL,8,Frates per thousand people of personal
OL,9,Frobbery and theft from the person in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales, among which phone
OL,11,Fthefts are a "significant" problem.
OL,13,FFigures released under Freedom of
OL,14,FInformation legislation show only a
OL,15,Ffraction of devices taken in London
OL,16,Fare returned to their owners.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
