PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781536274
OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FBetween 2017 and February 27 2024, a
OL,8,Ftotal of 587,498 phones were stolen in
OL,9,FLondon, excluding the City, 13,998 of
OL,10,Fwhich were recovered, and 573,500 were
OL,11,Fnot.
OL,13,FSusan Hall, the leader of the City
OL,14,FHall Conservatives, said that Sir
OL,15,FSadiq "should spend more time trying
OL,16,Fto fix things as opposed to saying 'la
OL,17,Fla la la la', I'm not listening,
OL,18,Feverything's fine'."
OL,26,@wD@GOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
