PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781536274
OL,3,CMayor in Singapore: #7m promotion
OL,4,Ccampaign to tackle online
OL,5,C'disinformation'
OL,7,FReform UK's candidate for Mayor of
OL,8,FLondon, Laila Cunningham, said: "If
OL,9,Fthe Mayor of London wants to encourage
OL,10,Fmore tourism, he should deal with the
OL,11,Fcrime he has allowed to spiral out of
OL,12,Fcontrol instead of suggesting that
OL,13,Fvictims of crime are liars."
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
